1
00:00:36,640 --> 00:00:37,880
Let me tell you

2
00:00:38,039 --> 00:00:39,280
That Wang Yingrong

3
00:00:39,439 --> 00:00:40,759
Just look at her

4
00:00:41,039 --> 00:00:42,280
She's a vixen reincarnated

5
00:00:42,439 --> 00:00:44,000
She won't let any man go

6
00:00:44,240 --> 00:00:45,479
Even ex-convicts

7
00:00:46,520 --> 00:00:47,159
Exactly

8
00:00:47,600 --> 00:00:49,240
That's why I was wrongly accused

9
00:00:49,439 --> 00:00:51,039
I got fired from the factory because of her

10
00:00:51,240 --> 00:00:52,439
Who can I complain to?

11
00:00:56,159 --> 00:00:57,600
You... what are you doing?

12
00:00:57,600 --> 00:00:58,399
Hitting my Old Zhang!

13
00:00:58,920 --> 00:01:00,439
That'll teach you to run your mouths!

14
00:01:00,799 --> 00:01:01,920
Do you think I'm easy to mess with?

15
00:01:01,960 --> 00:01:03,240
We saw it with our own eyes!

16
00:01:03,240 --> 00:01:04,200
We didn't lie!

17
00:01:04,439 --> 00:01:05,120
That's right!

18
00:01:05,159 --> 00:01:06,280
Which eye did you see it with?

19
00:01:06,519 --> 00:01:08,120
You dare do it but won't let people talk?

20
00:01:09,120 --> 00:01:09,799
Haiyang

21
00:01:11,599 --> 00:01:12,159
Brother Zheng

22
00:01:13,040 --> 00:01:14,959
We have nothing against you

23
00:01:15,319 --> 00:01:16,400
We all know it was

24
00:01:16,400 --> 00:01:18,079
Wang Yingrong who seduced you

25
00:01:18,359 --> 00:01:19,799
She... she's just shameless

26
00:01:21,200 --> 00:01:21,920
Hitting people again!

27
00:01:22,040 --> 00:01:23,159
I'm warning you

28
00:01:23,359 --> 00:01:24,840
Don't think about ruining a woman's reputation

29
00:01:25,159 --> 00:01:26,959
You know who I am

30
00:01:27,239 --> 00:01:28,239
If you really provoke me

31
00:01:28,719 --> 00:01:30,040
You'll pay for it

32
00:01:36,239 --> 00:01:37,879
You're so unreasonable

33
00:01:40,879 --> 00:01:41,480
Little Sister

34
00:01:41,640 --> 00:01:42,519
You're still young

35
00:01:43,000 --> 00:01:45,040
Studying is the most important thing now

36
00:01:45,239 --> 00:01:46,439
Not dating

37
00:01:46,799 --> 00:01:47,439
Mom

38
00:01:47,680 --> 00:01:49,560
Stop expecting so much from me

39
00:01:49,840 --> 00:01:51,719
I have my own life to live

40
00:01:52,120 --> 00:01:53,200
Just trust me

41
00:01:53,640 --> 00:01:55,400
I'll earn lots of money

42
00:01:55,680 --> 00:01:56,879
Marry into Hong Kong, China

43
00:01:57,200 --> 00:01:58,439
And take you and Dad there too

44
00:01:58,760 --> 00:02:00,560
To live the high life

45
00:02:01,239 --> 00:02:02,920
I've seen that boyfriend of yours

46
00:02:03,040 --> 00:02:03,959
I asked around about him

47
00:02:04,120 --> 00:02:05,280
He's not reliable at all

48
00:02:05,719 --> 00:02:07,000
He's just a playboy

49
00:02:07,159 --> 00:02:08,439
He has so many girlfriends

50
00:02:08,680 --> 00:02:10,000
If not ten, then nine

51
00:02:10,520 --> 00:02:12,240
And you're thinking of marrying him?

52
00:02:12,560 --> 00:02:13,599
And taking you to Hong Kong, China?

53
00:02:15,680 --> 00:02:17,479
You just can't stand me doing better than you

54
00:02:17,879 --> 00:02:18,560
Wang Yingtang

55
00:02:18,960 --> 00:02:20,680
Is there something wrong with your head?

56
00:02:20,879 --> 00:02:22,639
You missed the exam last time

57
00:02:22,800 --> 00:02:24,120
Probably because you were dating

58
00:02:24,199 --> 00:02:25,599
I think you brought this on yourself

59
00:02:25,719 --> 00:02:26,639
You're talking nonsense!

60
00:02:26,840 --> 00:02:28,199
I'll teach you to talk nonsense!

61
00:02:28,319 --> 00:02:29,680
You're wrong and you still hit me?

62
00:02:29,879 --> 00:02:32,319
I brew and sell vinegar every day

63
00:02:32,400 --> 00:02:33,759
Mom gives all the money I earn to you

64
00:02:33,800 --> 00:02:35,120
You ungrateful wretch

65
00:02:36,080 --> 00:02:36,919
You shameless thing

66
00:02:36,919 --> 00:02:38,159
I'll tear your mouth apart

67
00:02:38,479 --> 00:02:40,199
You dare curse your sister?

68
00:02:40,400 --> 00:02:41,000
Your wings...

69
00:02:48,400 --> 00:02:49,560
With those words you just said...

70
00:02:49,759 --> 00:02:51,120
you're disregarding your sister's innocence.

71
00:02:51,240 --> 00:02:52,800
Do you want your sister to die?

72
00:02:53,919 --> 00:02:54,879
Exactly.

73
00:02:58,199 --> 00:02:59,120
Mom.

74
00:03:00,759 --> 00:03:02,759
Little Sister was in the wrong first.

75
00:03:03,039 --> 00:03:04,719
She started it.

76
00:03:05,120 --> 00:03:06,360
But she is your sister.

77
00:03:06,639 --> 00:03:08,080
You should yield to her.

78
00:03:08,599 --> 00:03:09,080
Also,

79
00:03:09,199 --> 00:03:11,439
about that brewing and selling vinegar...

80
00:03:12,719 --> 00:03:14,240
why are you making such a fuss?

81
00:03:14,759 --> 00:03:15,759
Don't you know?

82
00:03:15,879 --> 00:03:17,680
Your second aunt brewed vinegar.

83
00:03:18,080 --> 00:03:18,719
And the result?

84
00:03:19,039 --> 00:03:19,960
One went mad.

85
00:03:20,199 --> 00:03:21,080
One died.

86
00:03:21,360 --> 00:03:22,879
Now you want to open a Vinegar Workshop.

87
00:03:22,960 --> 00:03:25,159
You're going to drag our whole family down.

88
00:03:27,960 --> 00:03:28,759
Mom.

89
00:03:29,759 --> 00:03:30,960
In your eyes,

90
00:03:31,759 --> 00:03:33,599
whatever Little Sister does is right.

91
00:03:34,159 --> 00:03:35,639
Whatever I do is wrong.

92
00:03:41,400 --> 00:03:42,360
What a sin.

93
00:03:42,759 --> 00:03:45,159
How did I give birth to a daughter like you?

94
00:03:52,360 --> 00:03:54,400
That second daughter of the Wang family

95
00:03:54,680 --> 00:03:56,360
is opening a Vinegar Workshop again.

96
00:03:56,639 --> 00:03:59,199
She simply doesn't know her limits.

97
00:03:59,520 --> 00:04:01,439
Let's see how she ends up.

98
00:04:01,840 --> 00:04:03,400
Those three daughters of the Wang family,

99
00:04:03,520 --> 00:04:04,960
not one is sensible.

100
00:04:05,319 --> 00:04:07,080
One is honest and timid,

101
00:04:07,400 --> 00:04:09,039
bullied by her in-laws.

102
00:04:09,240 --> 00:04:10,199
There's another one,

103
00:04:10,319 --> 00:04:11,400
is a shrew,

104
00:04:11,639 --> 00:04:12,759
causing all sorts of trouble.

105
00:04:13,120 --> 00:04:13,879
And the other one,

106
00:04:14,039 --> 00:04:15,560
couldn't even get into college.

107
00:04:15,840 --> 00:04:17,439
Good thing I gave birth to sons.

108
00:04:17,639 --> 00:04:19,279
My, Chen Xuelin's sons,

109
00:04:19,439 --> 00:04:20,839
are all obedient.

110
00:04:22,839 --> 00:04:24,560
I'm telling the three of you,

111
00:04:24,759 --> 00:04:25,240
from now on,

112
00:04:25,399 --> 00:04:27,399
don't associate with that Wang Yingrong.

113
00:04:27,959 --> 00:04:29,120
A girl making vinegar,

114
00:04:29,120 --> 00:04:30,959
sounds like improper business.

115
00:04:32,360 --> 00:04:33,160
Got it.

116
00:04:33,639 --> 00:04:34,519
Your big brother

117
00:04:34,600 --> 00:04:37,519
arranged jobs for you with Boss Tang.

118
00:04:45,600 --> 00:04:46,639
So work hard.

119
00:04:46,800 --> 00:04:47,800
Follow your big brother

120
00:04:48,079 --> 00:04:49,560
and work dutifully.

121
00:04:50,040 --> 00:04:50,600
As for me,

122
00:04:50,879 --> 00:04:52,160
I'll arrange marriages for you.

123
00:04:53,319 --> 00:04:53,639
Mom,

124
00:04:54,000 --> 00:04:55,199
I'm going to the factory to take a look.

125
00:04:57,600 --> 00:04:58,800
Eat before you go.

126
00:05:19,399 --> 00:05:20,439
We're out of grain.

127
00:05:21,199 --> 00:05:22,439
You don't need to go to the Vinegar Workshop.

128
00:05:23,360 --> 00:05:25,000
Just go do whatever you need to do.

129
00:05:25,959 --> 00:05:27,439
If you have other opportunities,

130
00:05:27,800 --> 00:05:29,360
you don't have to run the Vinegar Workshop with me.

131
00:05:30,040 --> 00:05:31,079
Your big brother

132
00:05:31,839 --> 00:05:33,360
can find jobs for you too.

133
00:05:35,240 --> 00:05:36,439
Running a Vinegar Workshop isn't easy.

134
00:05:37,000 --> 00:05:37,839
The risk is high too.

135
00:05:40,319 --> 00:05:41,360
Thinking of giving up, are you?

136
00:05:46,319 --> 00:05:47,600
Who wants to give up?

137
00:05:59,360 --> 00:06:00,160
Stubborn.

138
00:06:08,439 --> 00:06:09,720
I just feel that I...

139
00:06:09,720 --> 00:06:10,720
am quite useless.

140
00:06:11,439 --> 00:06:12,720
I can't get things done.

141
00:06:13,519 --> 00:06:14,800
I'm not likable.

142
00:06:15,519 --> 00:06:16,920
Like I've lived twenty years for nothing.

143
00:06:19,199 --> 00:06:20,480
You might be lacking in getting things done,

144
00:06:22,800 --> 00:06:24,120
but you're still likable.

145
00:06:31,519 --> 00:06:32,720
With such thick skin,

146
00:06:33,000 --> 00:06:33,839
it shouldn't hurt, right?

147
00:06:43,360 --> 00:06:44,600
Regarding the grain,

148
00:06:45,240 --> 00:06:46,399
I will find a way to solve it.

149
00:06:47,600 --> 00:06:48,399
Do you trust me?

150
00:07:00,920 --> 00:07:01,519
Haiyang

151
00:07:02,120 --> 00:07:03,879
You must listen to your mom.

152
00:07:04,160 --> 00:07:06,600
Wang Yingrong is going to run that Vinegar Workshop.

153
00:07:06,839 --> 00:07:08,399
You need to stay far away from her.

154
00:07:08,519 --> 00:07:09,759
Don't get involved.

155
00:07:10,439 --> 00:07:11,000
Mom.

156
00:07:11,720 --> 00:07:13,199
I think Sister Yingrong is quite nice.

157
00:07:13,600 --> 00:07:14,399
Whether she's nice or not...

158
00:07:14,399 --> 00:07:16,600
...what does that have to do with our family?

159
00:07:17,000 --> 00:07:18,160
Of you three brothers...

160
00:07:18,439 --> 00:07:19,480
do you know...

161
00:07:19,720 --> 00:07:21,759
why Mom is specifically warning you?

162
00:07:22,240 --> 00:07:23,680
Because I know you.

163
00:07:23,959 --> 00:07:26,600
You're just too easily trusting of people.

164
00:07:26,720 --> 00:07:27,879
Too impulsive.

165
00:07:28,279 --> 00:07:29,040
Listen to Mom.

166
00:07:29,319 --> 00:07:31,160
Don't get mixed up with the Wang family.

167
00:07:31,439 --> 00:07:33,399
Stay away from that Wang Yingrong.

168
00:07:38,680 --> 00:07:40,439
Say something.

169
00:07:40,839 --> 00:07:41,319
Mom.

170
00:07:42,040 --> 00:07:43,120
I'm not a child anymore.

171
00:07:43,720 --> 00:07:44,959
Stop worrying about me all the time.

172
00:07:45,160 --> 00:07:47,439
Relax, I'll definitely stay on the right path.

173
00:07:47,720 --> 00:07:49,000
Raise a child for a hundred years,

174
00:07:49,199 --> 00:07:50,600
worry for ninety-nine.

175
00:07:51,399 --> 00:07:52,600
Being a mother like this...

176
00:07:52,959 --> 00:07:53,759
is it easy for me?

177
00:08:01,360 --> 00:08:02,319
So,

178
00:08:02,439 --> 00:08:04,800
you came to me today to borrow money?

179
00:08:05,160 --> 00:08:07,360
Sort of, but not exactly.

180
00:08:07,839 --> 00:08:09,639
We want to get grain from farmers on credit.

181
00:08:09,920 --> 00:08:10,920
After negotiating the amount,

182
00:08:11,319 --> 00:08:12,360
we wanted to discuss with you...

183
00:08:12,639 --> 00:08:14,240
having you advance the payment first.

184
00:08:14,759 --> 00:08:16,240
I can sign an agreement with you.

185
00:08:16,399 --> 00:08:17,879
Once that batch of vinegar is brewed,

186
00:08:17,879 --> 00:08:19,680
we'll use the revenue to cover your advance.

187
00:08:23,920 --> 00:08:25,240
You guys are impressive.

188
00:08:25,240 --> 00:08:26,800
You already know how to do pre-sales.

189
00:08:27,600 --> 00:08:28,439
You...

190
00:08:29,279 --> 00:08:30,120
agree?

191
00:08:30,759 --> 00:08:33,039
I'm just waiting for your Baliang Vinegar.

192
00:08:33,519 --> 00:08:34,200
We...

193
00:08:34,200 --> 00:08:36,080
are now grasshoppers tied to the same rope.

194
00:08:36,200 --> 00:08:37,639
Helping you is helping myself.

195
00:08:38,000 --> 00:08:39,200
How could I not agree?

196
00:08:39,240 --> 00:08:40,480
Of course I can.

197
00:08:40,720 --> 00:08:42,440
Thank you so much, Uncle Fang.

198
00:08:42,799 --> 00:08:43,519
If you want to give thanks,

199
00:08:43,519 --> 00:08:44,519
thank yourself.

200
00:08:44,759 --> 00:08:46,159
You've done so many kind things.

201
00:08:47,000 --> 00:08:48,159
Once you've drafted the agreement,

202
00:08:48,200 --> 00:08:49,519
come to our shop to get the money.

203
00:08:50,440 --> 00:08:51,440
Pleasure doing business.

204
00:08:51,799 --> 00:08:52,480
Pleasure doing business.

205
00:08:59,200 --> 00:09:00,080
Actually,

206
00:09:00,080 --> 00:09:01,559
we could collect a bit more.

207
00:09:01,720 --> 00:09:02,799
When the vinegar is brewed,

208
00:09:02,879 --> 00:09:04,240
we can deliver it to the farmers' homes one by one.

209
00:09:04,240 --> 00:09:05,080
To thank them.

210
00:09:05,559 --> 00:09:05,960
By the way,

211
00:09:06,039 --> 00:09:07,080
there's also Uncle Fang.

212
00:09:07,159 --> 00:09:08,639
I can give him a bigger discount.

213
00:09:08,840 --> 00:09:10,039
Since he needs a large quantity anyway,

214
00:09:10,159 --> 00:09:11,440
small profits and quick returns work fine.

215
00:09:11,919 --> 00:09:13,200
Once Baliang Vinegar grows bigger,

216
00:09:13,360 --> 00:09:14,720
we can organize more events.

217
00:09:17,240 --> 00:09:18,120
What do you think?

218
00:09:21,519 --> 00:09:22,360
You make the call.

219
00:09:28,919 --> 00:09:29,840
This time,

220
00:09:31,200 --> 00:09:32,600
thank you for the solution you came up with.

221
00:09:33,600 --> 00:09:34,240
It's...

222
00:09:34,639 --> 00:09:36,039
isn't it just because you're stupid?

223
00:09:54,120 --> 00:09:55,240
Why are you touching me?

224
00:10:09,399 --> 00:10:10,200
Wang Yingrong!

225
00:10:10,360 --> 00:10:11,200
Zheng Minjiang!

226
00:10:11,279 --> 00:10:11,919
You two!

227
00:10:11,919 --> 00:10:13,039
Get the hell out here!

228
00:10:13,200 --> 00:10:14,840
You dare to do it but won't admit it, huh?

229
00:10:15,120 --> 00:10:16,960
Shameless! Get the hell out here!

230
00:10:17,799 --> 00:10:18,399
Wang Yingrong!

231
00:10:19,639 --> 00:10:21,200
Yang Liu, what are you doing?

232
00:10:21,960 --> 00:10:22,759
Oh, great.

233
00:10:23,080 --> 00:10:24,919
You two are coming out together now.

234
00:10:25,320 --> 00:10:25,799
Fine.

235
00:10:26,039 --> 00:10:27,240
Since neither of you will admit it,

236
00:10:27,320 --> 00:10:28,879
I'm going to have it out with you today.

237
00:10:29,039 --> 00:10:30,480
Where did this crazy woman come from, yelling here?

238
00:10:30,840 --> 00:10:32,120
That's our former sister-in-law.

239
00:10:32,759 --> 00:10:33,559
Brother got married?

240
00:10:33,919 --> 00:10:34,759
The one who scammed a marriage before

241
00:10:35,240 --> 00:10:36,559
and ran off with the money

242
00:10:36,720 --> 00:10:37,879
Zheng Minjiang and I

243
00:10:38,000 --> 00:10:39,759
are a formally married couple

244
00:10:40,120 --> 00:10:42,519
That Wang Yingrong, while I was visiting my parents,

245
00:10:42,639 --> 00:10:44,200
seduced my husband, Zheng Minjiang

246
00:10:44,600 --> 00:10:46,480
The two of them were hooking up in broad daylight

247
00:10:46,639 --> 00:10:47,720
Isn't that just bullying?

248
00:10:47,759 --> 00:10:49,000
You shouldn't have been with anyone

249
00:10:49,200 --> 00:10:50,759
let alone the one from the Zheng family

250
00:10:52,480 --> 00:10:53,519
See that? Did you see that?

251
00:10:53,600 --> 00:10:55,360
Her own mother admitted it

252
00:10:55,559 --> 00:10:56,240
Wang Yingrong

253
00:10:56,320 --> 00:10:57,399
You are just a slut

254
00:10:57,759 --> 00:10:59,600
You got dumped by some wild man and had nowhere to go

255
00:10:59,600 --> 00:11:00,840
So you came back to sling mud

256
00:11:01,399 --> 00:11:02,960
I went out to hook up with wild men?

257
00:11:03,159 --> 00:11:04,440
I think you're the one with a guilty conscience

258
00:11:04,559 --> 00:11:05,879
Trying to turn around and bite me

259
00:11:06,120 --> 00:11:06,919
Me? Guilty?

260
00:11:07,279 --> 00:11:08,200
Don't "you" me

261
00:11:08,440 --> 00:11:09,559
Everyone, come and take a look

262
00:11:10,039 --> 00:11:10,399
I...

263
00:11:10,960 --> 00:11:12,399
These are all evidence

264
00:11:12,559 --> 00:11:14,000
What kind of photos are these?

265
00:11:15,000 --> 00:11:16,159
Real... It's real

266
00:11:16,159 --> 00:11:16,679
They really are together

267
00:11:16,679 --> 00:11:17,440
Everyone, take a look

268
00:11:17,559 --> 00:11:18,759
This is all evidence

269
00:11:19,360 --> 00:11:21,360
Now, the proof is solid

270
00:11:21,960 --> 00:11:23,679
One seduced a married man

271
00:11:25,000 --> 00:11:26,399
The other cheated on his wife

272
00:11:29,120 --> 00:11:30,120
Impossible

273
00:11:30,440 --> 00:11:31,840
Our two families have no dealings

274
00:11:32,000 --> 00:11:34,039
The Wang family caused Minjiang's dad's death

275
00:11:34,320 --> 00:11:35,440
Minjiang promised me

276
00:11:35,679 --> 00:11:37,080
that he would draw a line with the Wang family

277
00:11:37,159 --> 00:11:38,480
It's impossible for them to be together

278
00:11:38,840 --> 00:11:39,639
Mom

279
00:11:40,320 --> 00:11:41,600
Yingrong and I are neighbors

280
00:11:42,000 --> 00:11:44,039
It's normal to bump into each other coming and going

281
00:11:44,639 --> 00:11:45,559
These photos

282
00:11:46,080 --> 00:11:47,120
don't prove anything

283
00:11:48,039 --> 00:11:48,600
Mom

284
00:11:49,120 --> 00:11:51,240
I know I have no one back at my parents' home

285
00:11:51,559 --> 00:11:53,600
but you can't bully me like this

286
00:11:54,480 --> 00:11:55,320
In this matter

287
00:11:55,720 --> 00:11:57,200
it is Zheng Minjiang who wronged me

288
00:11:57,519 --> 00:11:59,120
If you don't give me an explanation today

289
00:11:59,240 --> 00:12:00,320
I'll go make a scene at his factory

290
00:12:00,440 --> 00:12:01,519
I'll go shout it in the streets

291
00:12:01,600 --> 00:12:02,879
and see how he shows his face after that

292
00:12:03,639 --> 00:12:05,679
It looks like what she's saying is true

293
00:12:05,799 --> 00:12:06,759
I really couldn't tell.

294
00:12:06,960 --> 00:12:09,240
The eldest Zheng looks respectable.

295
00:12:09,440 --> 00:12:11,879
But actually, he's full of dirty tricks.

296
00:12:12,080 --> 00:12:12,919
No way.

297
00:12:13,120 --> 00:12:15,080
I think this is the second Wang child's fault.

298
00:12:15,240 --> 00:12:17,279
When that factory leader's wife came to make a scene...

299
00:12:17,600 --> 00:12:18,480
Wasn't it her, too?

300
00:12:18,840 --> 00:12:20,919
What she says doesn't sound like a lie.

301
00:12:20,919 --> 00:12:23,919
Zheng Minjiang finally won Boss Tang's favor.

302
00:12:24,159 --> 00:12:26,559
If this thing with Yang Liu blows up...

303
00:12:27,320 --> 00:12:29,399
And makes him lose such a good job opportunity...

304
00:12:30,240 --> 00:12:31,000
It would be such a pity.

305
00:12:31,879 --> 00:12:33,919
If Yang Liu drags her name through the mud...

306
00:12:35,080 --> 00:12:36,639
In the future, at home or outside...

307
00:12:36,879 --> 00:12:37,840
She won't be able to hold her head up.

308
00:12:39,039 --> 00:12:40,600
She's endured enough already.

309
00:12:43,879 --> 00:12:44,879
I like him, but there's nothing going on between us.

310
00:12:47,159 --> 00:12:49,399
For a girl to say something like that...

311
00:12:50,480 --> 00:12:52,200
She has no sense of shame at all.

312
00:12:52,200 --> 00:12:53,159
It's disgraceful.

313
00:12:53,759 --> 00:12:56,039
Brother, she confessed!

314
00:12:59,080 --> 00:12:59,799
Wang Yingrong, you...

315
00:13:00,039 --> 00:13:01,240
If I like him, I like him.

316
00:13:01,840 --> 00:13:02,879
Why can't I say it?

317
00:13:04,759 --> 00:13:06,279
I was the one who pursued him.

318
00:13:07,080 --> 00:13:08,200
Just like he said...

319
00:13:08,440 --> 00:13:09,679
There is nothing going on between us.

320
00:13:10,080 --> 00:13:11,240
It's just my one-sided wish.

321
00:13:12,639 --> 00:13:13,399
The two of us...

322
00:13:13,600 --> 00:13:14,600
Are worlds apart.

323
00:13:14,720 --> 00:13:15,679
We can never be together.

324
00:13:16,919 --> 00:13:18,759
She wants to tarnish her own name to protect me.

325
00:13:18,759 --> 00:13:20,080
So after all that...

326
00:13:20,080 --> 00:13:21,960
It was Yingrong's one-sided love.

327
00:13:22,320 --> 00:13:22,919
No.

328
00:13:22,960 --> 00:13:23,679
But...

329
00:13:25,519 --> 00:13:26,320
Yang Liu.

330
00:13:26,919 --> 00:13:28,519
What is your relationship with Zheng Minjiang now?

331
00:13:28,519 --> 00:13:29,679
You know it clearly yourself.

332
00:13:30,200 --> 00:13:32,080
You cheated him into marriage and took his money.

333
00:13:32,200 --> 00:13:33,360
You ran away the day after the wedding.

334
00:13:33,480 --> 00:13:34,679
Everyone in the neighborhood knows.

335
00:13:35,120 --> 00:13:36,720
Now that you've been dumped by a rich man...

336
00:13:36,720 --> 00:13:38,399
You finally decide to come back to Zheng Minjiang.

337
00:13:38,480 --> 00:13:39,799
What right do you have to lecture me?

338
00:13:40,279 --> 00:13:41,200
If you keep spouting nonsense...

339
00:13:41,200 --> 00:13:42,320
I'll rip your mouth apart!

340
00:13:45,320 --> 00:13:46,279
You came back to make a scene this time...

341
00:13:46,799 --> 00:13:47,919
Just to spread rumors and cause trouble?

342
00:13:48,399 --> 00:13:49,519
I don't think so.

343
00:13:50,440 --> 00:13:51,320
You threatened me...

344
00:13:51,480 --> 00:13:52,720
That you'd go make a scene at the factory.

345
00:13:53,440 --> 00:13:54,600
It's all just for money.

346
00:13:55,200 --> 00:13:56,120
Let me tell you.

347
00:13:56,519 --> 00:13:57,759
You won't get a single cent.

348
00:13:59,559 --> 00:14:01,279
So you cheated on him, too.

349
00:14:01,279 --> 00:14:03,519
You ran away from your marriage to hook up with a boss.

350
00:14:03,519 --> 00:14:05,080
Running away just to hook up with a boss...

351
00:14:05,080 --> 00:14:05,879
Truly shameless.

352
00:14:06,120 --> 00:14:07,279
You're the one who seduced my husband!

353
00:14:07,279 --> 00:14:07,960
Yang Liu!

354
00:14:09,279 --> 00:14:10,279
If I hear...

355
00:14:10,480 --> 00:14:11,759
One more rumor coming out of your mouth...

356
00:14:12,080 --> 00:14:13,120
About me and Yingrong...

357
00:14:14,039 --> 00:14:15,720
I promise you won't have an easy life.

358
00:14:16,720 --> 00:14:18,200
Exactly, exactly.

359
00:14:18,200 --> 00:14:19,559
How can you spread rumors like that?

360
00:14:22,720 --> 00:14:23,559
Tell me...

361
00:14:23,720 --> 00:14:24,399
Why...

362
00:14:24,559 --> 00:14:26,639
Do you have to get involved with that woman?
